<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .caption {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h1>Oops! Page Not Found</h1>
        <p class="error-message">It seems the page you are looking for has gone incognito.</p>
        <img src="/images/404.png" alt="404 Error - Page Not Found" class="error-image"/>
        <p class="caption">"Our detective couldn't crack this case either!"</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
